{"tid":2154785,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"為何要清理「微信」-陶傑","createTime":"2020-08-13T10:25:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T10:27:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"371d80c910a4f0d98df7e462a9bbf888eab89096","tid":2154785,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T10:25:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200718/JXHAKCUXX5DVLNPIIMWE2ABIII/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200718%2FJXHAKCUXX5DVLNPIIMWE2ABIII%2F&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzgx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=611dabb6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200718%2FJXHAKCUXX5DVLNPIIMWE2ABIII%2F&h=fee45f26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200718/JXHAKCUXX5DVLNPIIMWE2ABIII/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n為何要清理「微信」-陶傑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2LRxzDOQ8OxthCpiKl4SP23p860=/2587x1724/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/T2BR4TV3YBHKNHCVJWV7VKXCI4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2LRxzDOQ8OxthCpiKl4SP23p860%3D%2F2587x1724%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FT2BR4TV3YBHKNHCVJWV7VKXCI4.jpg&h=12cc32dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n川普為什麼下令禁了「剔托」、又禁「微信」。<br />\n<br />\n「剔托」是心智未成熟之。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n至於驅逐「微信」，則由生意金錢着眼。「微信」可以電子支付，接通中國的支付寶。美國有中國人多達五百萬，只「留學生」已三十七萬。中國人在美國，有自己的唐人街式消費圈：餐館和雜貨店，同文同種同氣連枝的自己抱團埋堆。在中國人開設的餐館商店，看見「自己人」上門幫襯，就叫他們用「微信」支付寶網絡付款，人民幣交收。該中國人老闆，在深圳北京什麼的另有家屬，看管大陸的銀行人民幣帳戶，交收雙方，人都在美國，應該履行公民義務、向美國政府和州政府納消費稅，卻分文全部不必繳交。<br />\n<br />\n在美國人眼中，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\nWell，現在美國的鄉。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n若去了美國，還極大倚賴「微信」和「百度」，上網看中央台電視劇集，以及與大陸的朋友親戚和校友拉群，健康心靈雞湯、春晚精彩片段、追看香港肥佬黎之蘋果傳媒評論和專欄，還有據說的長江水災不知是不是電腦合成的種種塌樓水淹的視頻，傳來傳去，「微信」不但令美利堅合眾國國中另有一國，「微信」還令美國華人仍然留在華文世界，無法融入主流。<br />\n<br />\n好處是少了許多抑鬱症， 。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n但川普不理，。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"34f036f9bc5c7dc57288f0b2f8151bb60ed880cf","tid":2154785,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T10:27:21.000Z","msg":"聯署支持封殺微信同TikTok<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fwe-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzgx%2F1T5MpBrdTD4T%2Fai5QWg%3D&h=4978d3d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/we-people-support-ban-wechat-and-tiktok</a>"}]}